{"tid":289634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[玄牛]長沙灣唐樓失火濃煙沖天　男住客受傷送院","createTime":"2017-06-19T07:27:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T13:00:21.000Z","uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"36cca79770c097f3dce9ced967349a447d624a0a","tid":289634,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T07:27:16.000Z","msg":"長沙灣永隆街及順寧道交界一幢唐樓，下午2時許，有途人發現唐樓的3樓突然起火，火舌由窗門捲出，大量濃煙沖上半空。消防接報到場救援，初步消息，1名男住客受傷送院。據了解，現場為一座已被收購的大廈，大部住客已遷出。<br />\n<br />\n讀者方先生指，當時在家中望出窗外看到大量濃煙，發現介乎寶熙苑與保安道街市之間的一幢唐樓的3樓起火，濃煙向上蔓延至4樓，他形容「啲煙好勁，好大煙呀！」其後更聽到「嘭」一聲爆炸聲，有碎片跌出街外，幸當時已封路，現場有2輛警車、數輛消防車，但未見有救護車。<br />\n<br />\n運輸署宣布，受火警影響以下路段封閉，包括永隆街近順寧道的唯一行車線，以及順事道介乎永隆街及東京街之間的全線。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170619/mobile/bkn-20170619144218422-0619_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170619%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170619144218422-0619_00822_001.html&d=gmxCWHuDPyNWqF10Ebo8y9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=95fc27c6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170619/mobile/bkn-20170619144218422-0619_00822_001.html</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n長沙灣撚表示 同一棟唐樓早兩個月先燒完<br />\n好似明顯咗d喎&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d6ba31287a423cd6ff9f6740e7211d255d93a4","tid":289634,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T07:30:37.000Z","msg":"玄牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f87554918e85ee8176ba043e4365eb579c9f80e","tid":289634,"uid":23707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T07:34:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7f1b3f3744e2b1dbdfcde66e545230872cd68d8","tid":289634,"uid":59443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T07:34:41.000Z","msg":"做做埋埋咁多陰騭野"},{"pid":"8433373faa3d3a6b7c766c5b6e02e3ddef68fa71","tid":289634,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco